com.gerken.gumbo.graph

Class GraphNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gerken.gumbo.graph.GraphNode

  • public class GraphNode
extends Object
    Represents a node in the graph A GraphNode has knowledge of the position of the node with respect to other nodes before and after it in the graph.
    Author:
    chrisgerken
